# Online Complaint Registration and Management System

This project is an Online Complaint Registration and Management System designed to simplify the process of submitting, managing, and resolving complaints for users, agents, and administrators.

## 🔍 Project Overview

The system offers a platform where users can register complaints online, track their progress, and communicate with the assigned agents. Agents handle the resolution, and administrators manage the entire workflow through dashboards.

This Full Stack application is developed using the *MERN* stack:
- *MongoDB* – For database
- *Express.js* – Backend framework
- *React.js* – Frontend library
- *Node.js* – JavaScript runtime for backend

